<geoCoordinate degrees="48" direction="west" minutes="31" orientation="longitude" precision="15" seconds="47" value="-48.52972">48°31'47&quot;W</geoCoordinate>
), in the Santa Catharina Island, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Florianópolis">Florianopolis</normalizedToken>
